Package: rfml
Type: Package
Title: MarkLogic Server in-database analytics for R
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Date: 2015-12-15
Author: Mats Stellwall [aut, cre]
Authors@R: person("Mats", "Stellwall", email = "mats.stellwall@gmail.com",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Functionality required to efficiently use R with MarkLogic Server.
    Many basic and complex R operations are pushed down into the database, which
    removes the main memory boundary of R and allows to make full use of MarkLogic
    server.
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
